        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The scheme &amp;quot;Assistance in Packing Materials under Post Harvest Management of Horticultural Produce&amp;quot; introduced by the Agriculture, Farmers Welfare and Cooperation Department, Gujarat,  aims to support farmers by providing financial aid for packing materials used in post-harvest stages to maintain quality and reduce losses. \n",
        "benefits_md": "\n   1. **Unit Cost:** ₹10,000/ha.    1. 75% of the cost or ₹7,500/hectare, whichever is less.\n\n&lt;br&gt;\n\n&gt; **Note:**\n\n\n   1. Corrugated boxes, wooden boxes will be used as packing material.\n   1. Assistance will be available up to a maximum limit of 1 hectare per account. \n   1. Available on i-Khedut portal every year (once during the year),\n\n",
        "briefDescription": "The scheme provides financial assistance to farmers to procure packing materials like corrugated and wooden boxes for post-harvest management of horticultural produce.\n\n",
        "exclusions_md": "<br>\n\n",
